mainText:
Although I never met Steve Jobs, I always enjoyed reading about how he had created a company as large as Apple from nothing. 

I sit here, saddened about this news in a way I never thought possible. I would like to thank Steve Jobs for all the hours he has put into bringing all these amazing products to the wider public and for achieving all that he has throughout his life. Without Steve Jobs, the world would not be what it is today.

My thoughts and prayers go to his family and to the whole of Apple Inc.&nbsp;
